name: 5 coins to pass (Browser Edition)
description:
This is a browser edition for 5_coins_to_pass.

The original game was made for NUS GDG's Week 5 Game Jam.

Group members: Jiale (Flamboyyy), Yibai (0-yibai), Neel (zawedcvg)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A game where you need 5 coins to pass each level! 

It may not be as simple as it looks!

Credits:

- Main assets: https://analogstudios.itch.io/

- BGMs: https://youtu.be/raWC6QsOROU, https://youtu.be/kazejfCyqx0

- Sound effects: https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/
